    answer: "Yes, good tattoo booking systems include image upload features so clients can share reference images, placement photos, and design ideas when they book. This gives you everything you need before the consultation—concept inspiration, size preferences, budget expectations, and placement. Images are organized per booking (not lost in DM threads) and accessible on both mobile and desktop for your design work.",
    links: [
      { text: 'Reference upload features', url: '/' },
