  <!-- Featured Answer -->
  <FeaturedAnswer question="What is a tattoo booking app?">
    A tattoo booking app lets clients book appointments, submit design references, and pay deposits from their phone, instead of a back-and-forth in Instagram DMs. With MyTattoo.Software, clients need no account: they leave their contact details, submit an intake form with reference images, and the artist reviews the request and offers a time slot with a deposit amount. Once the client pays that deposit through Stripe, the appointment is confirmed and added to the artist's calendar.
  </FeaturedAnswer>

