            <li><a href="#features" class="hover:text-brand-red">→ Essential Features</a></li>
            <li><a href="#benefits" class="hover:text-brand-red">→ Benefits for Artists</a></li>
            <li><a href="#benefits-of-app" class="hover:text-brand-red">→ Benefits of a Tattoo Booking App</a></li>
